title: Weds Post Show (03-02-22)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show (03-02-22)
description:
Bobby starts by giving Amy a hard time about getting a lot of endorsement requests. Bobby shares the full story behind why he was in Palm Springs and Las Vegas in the last week. Bobby shares some jokes he used at this ReMax even he spoke at earlier in the week. Bobby shares a story who almost missed out on her lottery winning because she thought it was a spam call and a man who was tased at an Orlando Airport.
